item.title: [HBASE-12059] Create hbase-annotations module
item.description: Different versions of hadoop have different annotations. We can smooth this out by providing our own.

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are closed can be reopened.

comments.comment:
Different versions of hadoop have different annotations. We can smooth this out by providing our own.

Have examples Elliott Clark? What pain we saving ourselves doing this sir?

Patch seems fine to me. Should get it into 0.99 if we are going this route.
